      "correctOptionId": "d",
      "explanation": "All options are valid ways to format strings, but f-strings (Option A) are the most modern and preferred way in Python 3.6+."
    },
    {
      "id": "q5",
      "text": "What is the purpose of the `__init__` method in a class?",
      "options": [
        { "id": "a", "text": "To initialize the class" },
