        { "id": "c", "text": "[0, 2, 4]" },
        { "id": "d", "text": "[2, 4]" }
      ],
      "correctOptionId": "c",
      "explanation": "`range(5)` generates 0, 1, 2, 3, 4. The condition `x % 2 == 0` filters for even numbers: 0, 2, 4."
